The paper discusses the use of crowdsourcing for complex computer tasks such as image tagging and natural language processing, which are typically associated with human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of crowdsourcing for sentiment analysis (cs.IR) and image annotation (cs.CL). Finally, the paper discusses the design and implementation of a framework for crowdsourcing data analytics (cs.SI).
